instruction: Generate a table summarizing the growth rate of the space economy, the occupancy elasticity, and the growth rates of returns and costs for the high-growth free-elasticity parameter set, the low-growth free-elasticity parameter set, and the mean-growth, low-elasticity and high-elasticity parameter sets.
output:
| Parameter Set | Growth Rate of Space Economy | Occupancy Elasticity | Growth Rates of Returns and Costs |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| High-Growth Free-Elasticity | 10.4% | 0.5 | 5.4% |
| Low-Growth Free-Elasticity | 5.4% | 0.5 | 5.4% |
| Mean-Growth, Low-Elasticity | 7.5% | 0.5 | 5.4% |
| Mean-Growth, High-Elasticity | 12.6% | 0.5 | 5.4% |

Note: The growth rates of returns and costs are the same for all parameter sets.
